- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image analysis and visual attributes.

- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as one of the applications mentioned is image retrieval.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes the use of learned visual attributes.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the interpretability of results for humans.
